## 📦 SDK Module Methods Reference

### Identity (Layer 0)
```typescript
registerIdentity(type, data)  → DID
getReputation(did)            → ReputationScore
generateProof(did)            → SignedProof
```

### Catalog (Layer 1)
```typescript
createProduct(data)           → ProductID
searchProducts(query, filters)→ Products[]
updateProduct(id, updates)    → Product
```

### Transaction (Layer 2)
```typescript
createOrder(items, buyer, vendor) → Order
initializePayment(orderId, method)→ PaymentInstructions
holdEscrow(orderId)               → EscrowRecord
releaseEscrow(orderId)            → Transaction
```

### Logistics (Layer 3)
```typescript
registerProvider(details)         → ProviderID
submitQuote(orderId, terms)       → Quote
updateTracking(shipmentId, status)→ Shipment
```

### Trust (Layer 4)
```typescript
openDispute(orderId, evidence)    → Dispute
submitRating(orderId, rating)     → Rating
checkSanctions(identity)          → SanctionCheck
```

### Governance (Layer 6)
```typescript
createProposal(action, params)    → Proposal
submitVote(proposalId, approve)   → Vote
executeProposal(proposalId)       → ExecutionResult
```

